Package com.binance4j.wallet.dto

Record Class CoinNetworkInformation

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.binance4j.wallet.dto.CoinNetworkInformation
Record Components:
addressRegex - The address pattern.
addressRule - Address rule
coin - The coin abbreviation.
depositDesc - The deposit description.
withdrawDesc - The withdra description.
name - The network name.
memoRegex - The memo pattern.
network - The network
specialTips - Tips about the network.
specialWithdrawTips - Tips about the withdraw.
depositDust - Deposit dust.
withdrawFee - The withdraw fee.
withdrawIntegerMultiple - Withdraw integer multiple
withdrawMax - The maximal amount authorized to be withdrawn.
withdrawMin - The minimal amount authorized to be withdrawn.
minConfirm - The min number for balance confirmation.
unLockConfirm - The confirmation number for balance unlock.
depositEnable - If deposit is enabled.
isDefault - if is the default network.
resetAddressStatus - Reset address status.
withdrawEnable - If withdraw is enabled.
sameAddress - If the coin needs to provide memo to withdraw.
